{"tid":1228654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們快back up","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T18:46:10.000Z","uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"72ab390857dd9c224027e80105b1ad26a92b4aef","tid":1228654,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"我同大家講，當送中條例撤回、港共政府高官下台、泛民係立法院拎到最多議席之後，我地就應該要清算班無良心嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">包括:   黑警<br />\n            所有諷刺受傷義士同死者嘅人</span><br />\n<br />\n           <br />\n唔同政見嘅就算鳩數，由得佢，叫佢地去大灣區發展，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無良心嘅人一定唔可以放過</span></span><br />\n<br />\n勞煩大家一齊back up <br />\n<br />\n仲有，去到依家呢個地步，仲自以爲清高、話中立嗰班人，你地應該感到羞愧，對自己嘅地方莫不關心，我屌你都嘥氣<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散<br />\n                      香港人一個都不能少    </span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申手機出post，排版可能好核突"},{"pid":"5611d212d247af511be67a4a6dce005e3b2c1000","tid":1228654,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"望緊post嘅黑警 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"e54c7c26feed07b75ebd2e7a1276c9cfa4a7d2c1","tid":1228654,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:55:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69b20baf0e155726d831b524bb3fba2ff0e5a99a","tid":1228654,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:55:12.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"1e665f844d11249befc0a4b364244498df77b35e","tid":1228654,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:00:14.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"8c754ffdba670739cfef6f4219aa42077163d485","tid":1228654,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:46:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}